message.body: How was the rest of your movie watching evening?
Good. Finished the movie, was passing out on the couch after. My mom came down and said "go to bed" hahah. Stayed up for a few more hours however. For some reason, I got up pretty early.
How was the rest of your night?
That's because you have steady rest now :) Uneventful. I was exhausted upon arriving at my apartment. I watched archer then passed out shortly after.
Now I'm reconsidering getting furniture today with the rain and such.
I think that can be put off till later if you don't mind living with all preferred furniture for now. At least Ewing until the weather gets nice.

It's just to organize the place. I wanted to grab my dresser and bookshelf so I'd have more counter space. My underwear is laid out in a suitcase for the time being. Things I want to display are sat on my desk.
Not yet. Yea, I would be excited/antsy to get my stuff set and and put away.
Wanna have dinner at Ikea later?
I'm picking up stuff from there. Figured might as well get their meatballs.
I have a birthday dinner tonight in University City. Thanks for the invite, enjoy the meatballs!
